  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Event Crew Member",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Event Crew Member</strong></h2><p><strong>On-Ground Sales • Brand Engagement • Real-World Experience</strong></p><p>Looking for work that keeps you moving, meeting people, and building confidence?<br />At <strong>Vision Organisation</strong>, this role puts you right in the action. You’ll be on the ground at events, roadshows, and campaigns, representing brands, engaging the public, and learning practical sales and communication skills through real experience.</p><p>This is <strong>not a desk-based role</strong>.<br />It’s for people who want to grow by doing.</p><h3><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Engage members of the public at events, roadshows, and campaign locations</p></li><li><p>Represent client brands in a professional, friendly, and confident manner</p></li><li><p>Communicate offers clearly and create positive customer experiences</p></li><li><p>Learn sales and communication skills through hands-on practice</p></li><li><p>Work closely with your team to support daily campaign objectives</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What You’ll Get</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Structured training provided. No prior experience required</p></li><li><p>Performance-based growth with clear development pathways</p></li><li><p>Earnings linked to effort and results</p></li><li><p>Ongoing coaching, feedback, and support</p></li><li><p>Exposure to different campaigns and working locations</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Who This Role May Suit</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Individuals who enjoy interacting with people</p></li><li><p>Those comfortable with active, on-ground work</p></li><li><p>Candidates open to learning, coaching, and self-improvement</p></li><li><p>Reliable team players who enjoy a fast-paced environment</p></li></ul><h3><strong>How to Apply</strong></h3><p>If you’re ready to gain hands-on experience in events, customer engagement, and sales, we’d be happy to connect.<br />📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507</p>",
